data.description: This beautiful two-story residence built in 2019 offers 5 beds, 3 baths and private 2 car garage. A large loft area allowing you to customize it as a playroom, office, or additional living space. This home is perfect for a growing family! The backyard provides a private oasis and a gated dog run, perfect for entertaining. No HOA! On a private street with minimal oncoming traffic. Situated in a newer community with growing amenities such as a new neighborhood park coming soon! Close to shopping, groceries and more! Don't miss out!
